---
import site from '../../site.config.json';
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---
<Page title="Privacy Policy" description={`How ${site.BRAND} handles your data.`}>
  <p>This policy describes what {site.BRAND} collects and why. Short version: as little as we can get away with, and we never sell it.</p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <p>If you give us your email address, we store it so we can send you the free download you asked for and occasional related emails. That's the only personal information we ask for. You can unsubscribe from any email using the link at the bottom of it, and unsubscribing removes you from our list.</p>

  <h2>Analytics and cookies</h2>
  <p>We use <strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> to see aggregate traffic — which pages get read, roughly where readers come from, and which tools get used. Google Analytics sets cookies in your browser when you allow it.</p>
  <p>We ask before doing that. Analytics cookies stay switched off until you accept them in the cookie banner, and if you decline, we only receive anonymous, cookie-less counts. You can change your mind by clearing this site's data in your browser. We do not use analytics to build advertising profiles of you.</p>

  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>Pages on this site may carry advertising. Where they do, our advertising partner and its vendors may set cookies or use similar technologies to measure and serve ads, subject to your choices above and to any consent tool they provide.</p>

  <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
  <p>Some links — mainly in our emails — are affiliate links, meaning we may earn a commission if you buy something through them, at no extra cost to you. Those links may pass a tracking identifier to the merchant so the referral is credited. This never changes what we recommend. See our <a href="/disclosure/">affiliate disclosure</a>.</p>

  <h2>Who else touches your data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>MailerLite</strong> — email delivery and list management.</li>
    <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — aggregate traffic measurement.</li>
    <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — hosting and delivery of this site.</li>
    <li>Our advertising partner, where ads are shown.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We don't sell or rent your personal information to anyone, and we never have.</p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>You can ask us what we hold about you, ask us to correct it, or ask us to delete it — including if you're covered by the GDPR or the CCPA. Send it through our <a href="/contact/">contact form</a> (pick "My data") and we'll action it. We don't charge for this and we won't make it difficult.</p>

  <h2>Children</h2>
  <p>This site isn't directed at children under 13 and we don't knowingly collect their information.</p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>If this policy changes materially, we'll update the date below.</p>

  <p><em>Last updated: July 2026.</em></p>
</Page>
